headline: The Honest Company’s (NASDAQ:HNST) Q2 Sales Beat Estimates But Stock Drops
summary: Personal care company The Honest Company (NASDAQ:HNST) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q2 CY2025, but sales were flat year on year at $93.46 million. Its GAAP profit of $0.03 per share was $0.02 above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Commerce Media Has Entered a New Era and IAB's Connected Commerce Summit Is Where It's Being Defined

As this new era reshapes how brands connect with consumers, the Interactive Advertising Bureau (IAB), the leading trade association for the digital advertising industry, will host its third annual IAB Connected Commerce Summit on Tuesday, September 9
